original_title: 1972 NSWRFL Grand Final: Manly Warringah Sea Eagles vs Eastern Suburbs Roosters
overview: After twenty-five years in the competition and five Grand Final losses, Manly finally broke through to win the club's first NSWRFL premiership.
title: 1972 NSWRFL Grand Final: Manly Warringah Sea Eagles vs Eastern Suburbs Roosters
